snippet.title: Minecraft PS3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Build! Craft! Explore!

http://us.playstation.com/games/minecraft-ps3.html

Discover a world with the freedom to do whatever you want. Dig down into the unknown depths or build incredible structures,
from humble homes to grand cityscapes. Go it alone or bring your friends along for the ride. The only limit is your imagination.

Published by Sony Computer Entertainment Europe. 'Minecraft' is a trademark of Notch Development AB. "PlayStation","PS3" and the "PS" Family logo are registered trademarks of Sony Computer Entertainment Inc. Greatness Awaits is a trademark of Sony Computer Entertainment America LLC.
